{
  "_instructions": [
    "Este arquivo é um template. Copie para google-service-account.json (sem .example)",
    "e preencha com os valores reais gerados no Google Play Console.",
    "",
    "Como gerar:",
    "  1. Google Play Console → Setup → API access",
    "  2. Link com um projeto Google Cloud (ou criar novo)",
    "  3. Create service account → Role: Release Manager",
    "  4. Manage keys → Add key → Create new key → JSON",
    "  5. Baixe o JSON e renomeie para google-service-account.json",
    "",
    "Nunca commite google-service-account.json (já está no .gitignore).",
    "Usado por: eas submit --platform android"
  ],
  "type": "service_account",
  "project_id": "seu-projeto-google-cloud",
  "private_key_id": "xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx",
  "private_key": "-----BEGIN RSA PRIVATE KEY-----\n...\n-----END RSA PRIVATE KEY-----\n",
  "client_email": "eas-submit@seu-projeto.iam.gserviceaccount.com",
  "client_id": "000000000000000000000",
  "auth_uri": "https://accounts.google.com/o/oauth2/auth",
  "token_uri": "https://oauth2.googleapis.com/token",
  "auth_provider_x509_cert_url": "https://www.googleapis.com/oauth2/v1/certs",
  "client_x509_cert_url": "https://www.googleapis.com/robot/v1/metadata/x509/eas-submit%40seu-projeto.iam.gserviceaccount.com",
